{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/929010/extras/ER.gif?t=1725622762\" /><br><br>Welcome to Swag and Sorcery, a new streamlined RPG from the creators of Punch Club and Graveyard Keeper! Build your own fantasy village, train and equip your heroes and send them out to collect Swag!<br><br><strong>Gameplay</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Equip your heroes<br></li><li>Send them out to fights (up to 3 parties at a time), and closely monitor the swag they get by progressing through levels<br></li><li>Pull them out of combat if they're about to die (otherwise they lose their loot)<br></li><li>Upgrade the heroes in your village and Repeat</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/929010/extras/swag.png?t=1725622762\" /><br><br><strong>Story</strong><br><br>Embark on an epic quest to retrieve the king's missing... suit. He really loves it. Wants it back. Let's put all the heroes into mortal danger for this important mission!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/929010/extras/Steam_Promo.gif?t=1725622762\" /><br><br>At its core Swag and Sorcery is an epic, ruthless adventure that both RPG and idle game fans will appreciate. There's also a sarcastic cat.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/929010/extras/Steam_Promo2_(1).gif?t=1725622762\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Recruiter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/929010/f046e1a58aba5199bd0561c94fe863e86ed73f99.jpg"},{"name":"Gorgeous Trinity","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/929010/76a327de529e02e7a7aea2ba914e0adab872b1d0.jpg"},{"name":"The more the merrier","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/929010/133447b5f